works.description:
The whole article "Andhra Bank Results  
2011 for PO and Clerks announced" starting from the text "Andhra Bank is  

one of the largest public sector bank in India recently conducted written 

examination for 450 Probationary officer and 1000 Clerk positions in this 

year. Andhra Bank PO recruitment written examination was held on
08.05.2011  
& Clerks recruitment written examination was held on 15.05.2011.
Candidates  
who given the written test now looking for the result. There are many  
candidates who given the exam are looking for their Andhra Bank Results  
2011, if you are one of them then don't worry because you are on right  
place. In this page you will get full information about this test and  
result.

Andhra Bank has selected the 1611 total no of candidates for the
interview.  
The final selection of PO Posts in Andhra Bank will announced after the  
interview.

Important Note for Bank Interview" and continuing till the end has been  
copied by the infringing blog
